sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083591 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.32-PM.png" alt="" width="1600" height="939" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.32-PM.png 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.32-PM-694x407.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.32-PM-1280x751.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.32-PM-768x451.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.32-PM-1536x901.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.32-PM-2048x1202.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ LEGO 官方圖片</p><p style="text-align: left;">打開 Sonic the Hedgehog – Green Hill Zone 積木套裝後，依舊有本說明書，印上 90 年代 Sonic 經典標誌。當然還有主角，6 大包和 1 小包 LEGO 積木，加上貼紙，為積本加上真實感，更能還原遊戲中的細節。<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083577 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06231.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06231.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06231-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06231-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲說明書</p><p style="text-align: left;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083579 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06234.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06234.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06234-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06234-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲6 大包和 1 小包 LEGO 積木</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1083578 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06233-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06233-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06233-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06233.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲貼紙</p><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">這盒組是</span> LEGO Ideas <span lang="ZH-TW">的最新項目，由</span> Sonic <span lang="ZH-TW">超級粉絲</span> Viv Grannell <span lang="ZH-TW">提出。她有感自己心愛的英雄人物會是老少咸宜的角色。</span>Viv <span lang="ZH-TW">表示：「</span>Sonic <span lang="ZH-TW">對不同人來說有多重意義，因為他夠靈活，能與時並進。</span>90 <span lang="ZH-TW">年代的創新突破、千禧年代帶來的刺激感，以及過去</span> 10 <span lang="ZH-TW">年的仁愛形象，統統反映了角色堅強、獨特且充滿魅力的性格。」</span></p></div><div></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">盒組包括一個</span> 90 <span lang="ZH-TW">年代經典造型的</span> Sonic <span lang="ZH-TW">人仔，還有以顆粒拼砌的</span> Moto Bug<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>Crabmeat <span lang="ZH-TW">及反派</span> Dr.Eggman<span lang="ZH-TW">。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083597 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06253.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06253.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06253-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06253-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Sonic、Moto Bug<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>Crabmeat <span lang="ZH-TW">及反派</span> Dr.Eggman</p><div><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083581 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06240.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06240.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06240-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06240-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Sonic</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083582 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06249.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06249.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06249-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06249-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Sonic</p><div><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083583 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06239.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06239.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06239-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06239-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-TW">▲反派</span> Dr.Eggman</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083584 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06247.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06247.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06247-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06247-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-TW">▲反派</span> Dr.Eggman</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083585 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06238.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06238.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06238-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06238-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-TW">▲反派</span> Dr.Eggman</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083586 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06242.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06242.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06242-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06242-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Moto Bug</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083587 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06243.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06243.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06243-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06243-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Moto Bug</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083590 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06250.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06250.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06250-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06250-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Moto Bug</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083588 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06241.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06241.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06241-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06241-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Crabmeat</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083589 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06251.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06251.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06251-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC06251-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Crabmeat</p></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">遊戲初次在</span> 1991 <span lang="ZH-TW">年推出時的關卡，現已成為遊戲史上的經典場景之一</span> -Green Hill Zone<span lang="ZH-TW">。</span><span lang="ZH-TW">沿途你要收集</span> 7 <span lang="ZH-TW">個金環，部分要利用彈弓台將</span> Sonic <span lang="ZH-TW">送上半空才能奪得，另外還有</span> 3 <span lang="ZH-TW">個電視形狀的</span> Item Boxes<span lang="ZH-TW">，包括 </span>Extra Life<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>Speed Shoes<span lang="ZH-TW">，以及</span> Blue Shield<span lang="ZH-TW">。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083599 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.46-PM-1.png" alt="" width="1600" height="888" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.46-PM-1.png 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.46-PM-1-694x385.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.46-PM-1-1280x711.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.46-PM-1-768x426.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.46-PM-1-1536x853.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot-2022-01-27-at-6.39.46-PM-1-2048x1137.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ LEGO 官方圖片</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083600 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074550241.jpeg" alt="" width="800" height="1016" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074550241.jpeg 800w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074550241-457x580.jpeg 457w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074550241-709x900.jpeg 709w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074550241-768x975.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ LEGO 官方圖片</p></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083601 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074551348.png" alt="" width="800" height="450" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074551348.png 800w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074551348-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074551348-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ LEGO 官方圖片</p></div><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/RESIZE_loops.bmp"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1083604 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/RESIZE_loops-694x486.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="486" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/RESIZE_loops-694x486.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/RESIZE_loops-1280x896.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/RESIZE_loops-768x538.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/RESIZE_loops.bmp 1337w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><div><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-TW">▲遊戲史上的經典場景之一 -Green Hill Zone</span></p><p><span lang="ZH-TW">玩過</span> Sonic <span lang="ZH-TW">的都知道，玩家的最終目標是保護</span> 7 <span lang="ZH-TW">顆</span> Chaos Emeralds<span lang="ZH-TW">。集齊所有寶石後，你便可將它們放在寶石座上展示。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1083598 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074552946.jpeg" alt="" width="800" height="697" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074552946.jpeg 800w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074552946-666x580.jpeg 666w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/164074552946-768x669.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ LEGO 官方圖片</p></div></p><div class="feedflare">
